content: Flawed execution of a good idea. Horrible controls
VERY NICE GAME I LOVE IT
Doesn't have everything from the PC version but it is still very good

Is a very great game. Very unique. Some DLC would be great. Green Berets setting up a a base doing missions and defending a base that comes more and more under attack as you finish missions. Missions using the US Army tunnel rats. Snatch and grab missions behind enemy lines and pow rescue.
Have you fixed the audio yet, I paid for premium but it cuts up the audio so bad I have a very hard time playing it
Not as good as id expected. Fantastic idea. But just didnt fill out to what i thought it would.
This game is awesome it's easy to handle it and a good story
The game is not designed for mobile devices, it is difficult to play the game when controls barely work.

Enjoyable so far, but some notes - The long press menu can clip off the screen depending on positioning & the game doesn't work with phone rotation. Please fox to unlock an extra star. I may revisit this review once I have played more.
The game is fun there is really not much to say about it I wish that when u put on microphone the guy u play as doesn't say it I still love the game and it will be a long time before I stop
